{"tid":1551094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周日遮打花園至美國領事館遊行　獲發不反對通知書","createTime":"2019-09-07T23:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T06:37:07.000Z","uid":50457,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9cecb4d1ead2dbb40ddb90cefedf29fc7131bfed","tid":1551094,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:29:45.000Z","msg":"有市民發起明日（9月8日）舉行公眾活動，由中環遮打花園遊行到美國駐港總領事館請願，有關集會遊行獲警方發出不反對通知書。 該活動名為「香港人權與民主祈禱會」，集會時間由下午1時30分至6時30分，地點為中環遮打花園，即場收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署，之後向美國駐港總領事館遞交。 美國國會將於9月9日復會，近日網上其中一個強烈訴求，是促請美國通過《香港人權及民主法案》。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-07-2019/55768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F09-07-2019%2F55768&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprl3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=b025122d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-07-2019/55768</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019"},{"pid":"e614e9306148f99511269a5a64f5296fd9546537","tid":1551094,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:42:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"484f74487dbf7a73495d0643f33fa9f86b9269c3","tid":1551094,"uid":183950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c1ec273d250c3de4eb5b5391956ce68d74bdbd","tid":1551094,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6bfdac1b127fc3e9eaaf8836602e7e3185def70","tid":1551094,"uid":192848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:28:41.000Z","msg":"幫所有p牌推行動post"},{"pid":"b2f0859760d3185f23247bf52fbaf7c5aadd5abe","tid":1551094,"uid":252182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:30:35.000Z","msg":"推呀推<img src=\"/a